", "contents_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/contents/gcc%2Ftestsuite%2Fgcc.c-torture%2Fexecute%2F20041218-2.c?ref=ca6af4f857cf2b93e89e99bad1dd2598c0b74f02", "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,15 @@\n+extern void abort (void);\n+\n+int test(int n)\n+{\n+  struct s { char b[n]; };\n+  n++;\n+  return sizeof(struct s);\n+}\n+\n+int main()\n+{\n+  if (test(123) != 123)\n+    abort ();\n+  return 0;\n+}"}]}